Hello and welcome to the Employee Management System. Please enter in the number
associated with an option below:
----------------------------------------------------------
|  (0) ---> Exit the application                         |
|  (1) ---> Read Employee/Department data                |
|  (2) ---> Update an Employee/Department                |
|  (3) ---> Delete Employee/Department data              |
|  (4) ---> Create a new Employee/Department             |
----------------------------------------------------------